{{Nihongo|'''''AIBOU: The Movie III'''''|相棒 -劇場版III-　巨大密室！特命係 絶海の孤島へ||Partners: The Movie III}} is a 2014 Japanese [[mystery film|mystery]] [[suspense film|suspense]] [[crime film|crime]] film directed by [[Seiji Izumi]]<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.allcinema.net/prog/show_c.php?num_c=347720|title= 相棒 -劇場版III-　巨大密室！特命係 絶海の孤島へ(2014)|accessdate= 2 May 2014|work= allcinema.net|publisher= Stingray|language= Japanese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.tokyohive.com/article/2014/05/japan-box-office-report-4-264-27|title= Japan Box Office Report – 4/26~4/27|date= 1 May 2014|accessdate= 2 May 2014|work= tokyohive|publisher= 6Theory Media, LLC}}</ref> and based on the television series ''[[AIBOU: Tokyo Detective Duo]]''.

==Cast==
*[[Yutaka Mizutani]]
*[[Hiroki Narimiya]]
*[[Tsuyoshi Ihara]]
*[[Yumiko Shaku]]
*[[Toru Kazama]] 

==Reception==
The film grossed US$19.8 million in Japan.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/japan/yearly/?yr=2014&sort=gross&order=DESC&pagenum=1&p=.htm|title= Japan Yearly Box Office 2014|accessdate= 28 October 2015|work= [[Box Office Mojo]]}}</ref>

